FEniCS course
-------------

1. Put slides as single .tex files in the 'slides' directory.

2. Put images in the 'pdf' and 'png' directories etc.

3. Build lectures by typing 'make'.

4. Copy overview.tex to a course-specific overview_foo_yyyy.tex
   and edit to suit course contents.

5. Upload lectures to fenicsproject.org/pub/course/

Note: if you get version mismatch errors for listings.sty,
edit mylistings.sty and replace the version number (currently 1.5c)
with your listings.sty installation version.

